high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove top on the left side of the room.
Pick up the pan from the stove top.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter top by the toaster.
Put the pan on the counter top, in front of and to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn around, walk, turn right to enter the kitchen, and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the front right burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and pick it up again.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the pan on the counter to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the left of the kitchen island, moving forward until you reach the stove on the left, then turn to face the stove.
Pick up the dirty skillet from the stove.
Turn around to your left and go to the sink.
Wash the skillet in the sink.
Face the opposite direction and go the the opposite counter.
Put the skillet on the counter above the dishwasher, to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean skillet on a counter to the right of a toaster.
